caption:
Happy 4th birthday to my silly, super smart, sweet little Drewsie. 🥳👶🏼

I am not sure how 4 years have passed since you made me a mommy and made dada a daddy but it has sped by in a literal blink. We truly can’t imagine life before you and you make us laugh every single day. This is the first year I think you really understand that it’s your birthday and it has been so much making you feel special all day.

Love you to the 🌙 and make, Drewgie boo.
